<section id="about">
  <div class="section-label">Who I Am</div>
  <div class="about-grid reveal">
    <div class="about-text">
      <h2 class="section-title">ABOUT<br>ME</h2>
      <p>I'm a <strong>creative and detail-oriented</strong> graphic designer and video editor currently pursuing B.Tech from C.S.J.M. University, Kanpur.</p>
      <p>I specialize in transforming ideas into visually compelling content — whether that's a brand identity, a YouTube video edit, or an eye-catching thumbnail. I'm passionate about storytelling through visuals and constantly exploring new design trends.</p>
